```{r CPU}
CPU <- read.csv("../final_data/CPU.csv")
CPU$ReleaseDate <- as.Date(CPU$ReleaseDate, format = "%Y-%m-%d")
CPU$CurrentDate <- as.Date(CPU$CurrentDate, format = "%Y-%m-%d")
CPU$Score <- as.numeric(CPU$Score)
CPU$X <- NULL
summary(CPU)
```
